source.name: Price Spreads From Farmer to Consumer
source.description: USDA Economic Research Service compares prices paid by consumers for food with prices received by farmers for corresponding commodities. This data set reports these comparisons for a variety of foods sold through retail foodstores such as supermarkets and supercenters.
